                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7109" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0174</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7668 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;粮&quot;苦用心：塞北粮仓的企业社会责任践行之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Grain&quot; Hard Heart: The Way to Practice Corporate Social Responsibility in Saibei Granary</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李友东，周烜利，王嘉琪，刘安然，闫晨丽，李冯亚，李鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古塞北粮仓农业发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">塞北粮仓；社会责任；粮食安全；扶贫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Saibei Granary; Social responsibility; Food security; Poverty alleviation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">塞北粮仓虽然是一家位于内蒙古地区的年轻中小企业，但是，公司从筹建之初便十分重视并以身作则地践行农业企业应承担的社会责任。以塞北粮仓的创立、发展历程为主脉络，讲述了董事长王宁创办塞北粮仓的初心以及带领公司团队对企业社会责任不同阶段的摸索、尝试及转变过程。在此过程中，王宁顶住压力、克服困难，先后解决了农村合作社与农户问题、股东结构不合理问题、未来发展道路问题。正是由于王宁在公司发展过程中时刻不忘社会责任，社会责任这颗种子才能经过多年的灌溉，终在每个塞北粮仓人心中生根发芽。由此以案例形式描述了中小企业履行社会责任的过程中可能面临的困境及解决方法，同时也诠释了公司高层在企业履行社会责任的过程中发挥的重要作用。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Although Saibei Granary is a young small and medium-sized enterprise located in Inner Mongolia, the company attaches great importance to and practices the social responsibility of agricultural enterprises by setting an example from the beginning of its establishment. Taking the establishment and development of Saibei Granary as the main context, it tells the original intention of Founding Saibei Granary by Chairman Wang Ning and the exploration, trial and transformation process of different stages of corporate social responsibility under the leadership of the company team. In this process, Wang Ning withstood pressure and overcame difficulties, and successively solved the problems of rural cooperatives and farmers, unreasonable shareholder structure and future development path. It is because Wang Ning always keeps social responsibility in mind during the development of the company that the seed of social responsibility can finally take root and sprout in the hearts of everyone in Saibei Granary after years of irrigation. This paper describes the difficulties and solutions that SMES may face in the process of fulfilling their social responsibilities in the form of cases, and also explains the important role of corporate executives in the process of fulfilling their social responsibilities.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理与企业社会责任》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任的概念类型；利益相关者理论；企业社会责任演化路径；组织韧性、企业社会责任与可持续商业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
